H0.text: Which disastrous amphibious landing in 1942 used British troops, Canadian troops and US Rangers. Salerno

H3.text: Which disastrous amphibious landing in 1942 used British troops, Canadian troops and US Rangers. Dieppe

A4.text: Operation Jubilee was a disastrous Allied amphibious attack on the German-occupied port of Dieppe in northern France.

A5.text: The raid included over 6,050 infantry, predominantly Canadian, supported by a regiment of tanks.
